description:
Nature's Way Adult Vita Gummies Multivitamin supports general health & wellbeing with essential vitamins and minerals.

Nature’s Way Adult Vita Gummies Multivitamin is formulated with 11 vitamins and minerals to help support: immune system health, energy production, heart health, nervous system function, healthy teeth and strong bones. This product also supports skin and hair health, nail strength and collagen formation. Best of all the great tasting strawberry flavoured gummies are so easy to take – no water and no swallowing difficult tablets.
